  "keyFeatures": [
    "38 builder + 38 reviewer skill pairs covering the full industrial robotics lifecycle",
    "Audit-ready xlsx workbook outputs with NAVY/Calibri styling and PLr/SIL color coding",
    "Chain compounding via stable xlsx contracts — upstream changes propagate automatically downstream",
    "Visual dashboard reviewer outputs with KPI tiles, pie charts, compliance bars, and findings tables",
    "Coverage of ISO 12100, ISO 13849-1, IEC 62061, ISO 10218-1/-2:2025, ISO/TS 15066, ISO 3691-4, IEC 62443",
    "ROS2 architecture artifacts including URDF, behavior trees, Nav2 config, and TF tree specs",
    "AI/ML governance artifacts: datasheets for datasets, model cards, and perception test catalogs",
    "IEC 62443 industrial cybersecurity risk assessment and OT asset inventory",
    "Bundled download of all 76 skills as a single zip file",
    "Compatible with Claude Desktop and Cowork via .skill file installation"
  ],
